<ol id="conformance">
<li><b>SHALL</b> contain exactly one [1..1] <tt><b>@classCode</b>="ENC" </tt> (CodeSystem:<tt> 2.16.840.1.113883.5.6 HL7ActClass</tt>)
</li>
<li><b>SHALL</b> contain exactly one [1..1] <tt><b>@moodCode</b>="EVN" </tt><i>Event</i> (CodeSystem:<tt> 2.16.840.1.113883.5.1001 HL7ActMood</tt>)
</li>
<li><b>SHALL</b> contain at least one [1..*] <tt><b>id</b></tt>
</li>
<li><b>SHOULD</b> contain exactly one [1..1] <tt><b>code</b></tt>, which <b>SHOULD</b> be selected from ValueSet<tt> 2.16.840.1.113883.1.11.13955 EncounterCode</tt><b> STATIC</b>
</li>
<li><b>MAY</b> contain zero or one [0..1] <tt><b>effectiveTime</b></tt>
</li>
<li><b>MAY</b> contain zero or more [0..*] <tt><b>entryRelationship</b></tt>, such that
<ol>
<li>Contains exactly one [1..1] <xref href="../PatientInstruction.dita">Patient Instruction</xref> (templateId: <tt>2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.1.49</tt>)</li></ol></li>
<li><b>MAY</b> contain zero or one [0..1] <tt><b>entryRelationship</b></tt>, such that
<ol>
<li>Contains <tt><b>@typeCode="</b>SUBJ" </tt><i>SUBJ (has subject)</i></li>
<li>Contains exactly one [1..1] <xref href="../AgeObservation.dita">Age Observation</xref> (templateId: <tt>2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.1.38</tt>)</li></ol></li>
<li><b>MAY</b> contain zero or more [0..*] <tt><b>encounterLocation</b></tt>, such that
<ol>
<li>Contains exactly one [1..1] <xref href="../EncounterLocation.dita">Encounter Location</xref> (templateId: <tt>2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.1.45</tt>)</li></ol></li>
<li><b>MAY</b> contain one or more [1..*] entryRelationship with @typecode='RSON' where target represents the indication for the activity</li>
<li><b>MAY</b> contain zero or more [0..*] performer, used to define the practioners involved in an encounter</li>
<li><b>MAY</b> contain one [0..1] performer / assignedEntity / code, to define the role of the practioner</li>
<li><b>SHALL</b> contain one or more sources of information</li>
</ol>
